msgid "List webhook endpoints"
msgstr "列出 Webhook 端點"

msgid "Get all configured webhook endpoints for this store."
msgstr "取得此商店設定的所有 Webhook 端點。"

msgid "Create webhook endpoint"
msgstr "建立 Webhook 端點"

msgid ""
"Create a new webhook endpoint.\n"
"\n"
"        The secret will be auto-generated and returned in the response.\n"
"        **Store the secret securely** - it will only be shown once.\n"
"\n"
"        Example events: `order.created`, `order.shipped`, `payment.received`"
msgstr ""
"建立新的 Webhook 端點。\n"
"\n"
"密鑰將會自動產生，並在回應中返回。\n"
"**請安全地儲存密鑰** - 它只會顯示一次。\n"
"\n"
"範例事件：`order.created`，`order.shipped`，`payment.received`"

msgid "Validation error"
msgstr "驗證錯誤"

msgid "Get webhook endpoint"
msgstr "取得 Webhook 端點"

msgid "Get details of a specific webhook endpoint."
msgstr "取得特定 Webhook 端點的詳細資訊。"

msgid "Endpoint not found"
msgstr "端點未找到"

msgid "Update webhook endpoint"
msgstr "更新 Webhook 端點"

msgid "Update an existing webhook endpoint."
msgstr "更新現有的 Webhook 端點。"

msgid "Delete webhook endpoint"
msgstr "刪除 Webhook 端點"

msgid "Delete a webhook endpoint. All delivery logs will also be deleted."
msgstr "刪除一個 Webhook 端點。所有遞送記錄也將被刪除。"

msgid "Endpoint deleted"
msgstr "端點已刪除"

msgid "Test webhook endpoint"
msgstr "測試 Webhook 端點"

msgid ""
"Send a test webhook to verify the endpoint configuration.\n"
"\n"
"    This sends a `test.webhook` event with sample data to verify\n"
"    that the endpoint is reachable and properly configured."
msgstr ""
"發送測試 Webhook 以驗證端點配置。\n"
"\n"
"這會傳送一個帶有範例資料的 `test.webhook` 事件，以驗證\n"
"端點是否可達且配置正確。"

msgid "Rotate webhook secret"
msgstr "輪換 Webhook 秘密"

msgid ""
"Generate a new secret for a webhook endpoint.\n"
"\n"
"    The new secret will be returned in the response. **Store it securely** "
"-\n"
"    it will not be shown again. You will need to update your webhook\n"
"    receiver to use the new secret."
msgstr ""
"為 Webhook 端點產生新的密鑰。\n"
"\n"
"新的密鑰將會在回應中返回。**請妥善儲存** -\n"
"它不會再次顯示。您需要更新您的 Webhook\n"
"接收端以使用新的密鑰。"

msgid "Reset endpoint failures"
msgstr "重置端點失敗"

msgid ""
"Reset the failure count for a webhook endpoint.\n"
"\n"
"    This re-enables an endpoint that was auto-disabled due to\n"
"    consecutive failures."
msgstr ""
"重置 Webhook 端點的失敗次數。\n"
"\n"
"這將重新啟用因連續失敗而自動停用的端點。"

msgid "List webhook deliveries"
msgstr "列出 Webhook 配送"

msgid "Get webhook delivery logs with optional filtering."
msgstr "取得 Webhook 遞送記錄，可選擇過濾。"

msgid "Filter by endpoint UUID"
msgstr "按端點 UUID 過濾"

msgid "Filter by event type (e.g., order.created)"
msgstr "按事件類型過濾（例如：order.created）"

msgid "Filter by delivery status"
msgstr "按配送狀態篩選"

msgid "Number of results to return (default 50, max 200)"
msgstr "要返回的結果數量（預設 50，最多 200）"

msgid "Get webhook delivery"
msgstr "取得 Webhook 配送"

msgid "Get details of a specific webhook delivery including the full payload."
msgstr "取得特定 Webhook 送達的詳細資訊，包括完整的負載。"

msgid "Delivery not found"
msgstr "未找到遞送"

msgid "Retry webhook delivery"
msgstr "重試 Webhook 遞送"

msgid ""
"Manually retry a failed webhook delivery.\n"
"\n"
"    This queues the delivery for immediate retry, regardless of\n"
"    the scheduled retry time."
msgstr ""
"手動重試失敗的 Webhook 交付。\n"
"\n"
"這會將交付排入佇列，立即重試，不論預定的重試時間為何。"

msgid "Cannot retry this delivery"
msgstr "無法重試此配送"

msgid "List webhook event types"
msgstr "列出 Webhook 事件類型"

msgid ""
"Get all available webhook event types.\n"
"\n"
"    Returns a list of events that can be subscribed to when\n"
"    creating a webhook endpoint."
msgstr ""
"取得所有可用的 Webhook 事件類型。\n"
"\n"
"返回可在建立 Webhook 端點時訂閱的事件清單。"

msgid "Get webhook documentation"
msgstr "取得 Webhook 文件"

msgid ""
"Get comprehensive documentation for webhook integration.\n"
"\n"
"    Returns all available event types, payload schemas, signature "
"verification\n"
"    instructions, and code examples for integrating with the webhook "
"system.\n"
"\n"
"    This endpoint is publicly accessible to allow external developers to\n"
"    understand webhook payloads without authentication."
msgstr ""
"取得 webhook 整合的完整文件。\n"
"\n"
"回傳所有可用的事件類型、負載結構、簽名驗證\n"
"指示，以及整合 webhook 系統的程式碼範例。\n"
"\n"
"此端點是公開可存取的，以讓外部開發人員\n"
"在不進行驗證的情況下了解 webhook 負載。"

msgid "Get webhook endpoint stats"
msgstr "取得 Webhook 端點統計資料"

msgid "Get delivery statistics for a webhook endpoint."
msgstr "取得 Webhook 端點的傳遞統計資料。"

