"Failed deliveries are retried with exponential backoff: 1 minute, 2 minutes, "
"4 minutes, 8 minutes, etc."
msgstr "失敗的配送會以指數退避方式重試：1 分鐘、2 分鐘、4 分鐘、8 分鐘等。"

